timezeros_novdec <- seq(from = as.Date("2020-11-01") , to = as.Date("2020-12-31"), by="days") 

truth_data_novdec <- load_truth(truth_source = "JHU", 
                         target_variable = "inc case", 
                         truth_end_date = "2020-12-31", 
                         locations = c("12", "48", "25", "36", "06", "26"))

forecasts_data_novdec <- load_forecasts(models = c("COVIDhub-baseline", "CU-select", 
                                            "OliverWyman-Navigator", "LANL-GrowthRate",
                                            "IowaStateLW-STEM", "JHU_IDD-CovidSP", "UVA-Ensemble"), 
                                 forecast_dates = timezeros_novdec,
                                 locations = c("12", "48", "25", "36", "06", "26"), 
                                 targets = paste(1:4, "wk ahead inc case"), 
                                 hub = "US")
